dct_description_sm: U.S. Geological Survey, George Otis Smith, Director; R.B. Marshall, Chief Geographer; Sledge Tatum, Geographer in charge; topography by A.P. Meade, Jr., and F.H. Nelson ; control by C.F. Urquhart and C.H. Semper.
